N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 68.12 - Releases from the delinquent list

State Regulations

The Authority may grant a release from the delinquent
(C.O.D.) list to any retail licensee who has received a notice of default or is
named on the delinquent (C.O.D.) list on good cause shown to it and after
investigation of the facts. Notes
